column2: SELECT u.up_name as [name],     p.objID, p.ra, p.dec,    dbo.fPhotoTypeN(p.type) as type,     p.modelMag_u, p.modelMag_g, p.modelMag_r, p.modelMag_i, p.modelMag_z,s.z as redshift,pmodelMag_z FROM #upload u       JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id       JOIN PhotoTag p ON p.objID = x.objID        LEFT JOIN SpecObjAll s p.ObjID = s.bestObjID WHERE     p.type = #  ORDER BY x.up_id
